race.description: Crowne Real Estate Geoff & Alley Hcp (Bm58)
race.comment: EMPIRE OF ART (5) wasn't disgraced in town at the latest effort and should find this assignment much more to his liking. Thompson stays on board following that last-start outing and maps ideally from gate two. Should be right there when the whips are cracking. SOUTHOFTHEBORDER (3) shed the maiden tag in impressive fashion last time out and will have derived a bunch of confidence from that dominant victory. Can go right on with the job now. DEMARCAY (2) was too bad to be true last time but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance from the inside alley. BRAVE BOY (1) boasts a win over this staying trip and will be at peak fitness for this. In the mix. KENSHIN MARU (6) next best with the 2kg claim.
